224
00:18:12,687 --> 00:18:16,521
Who am, I you
ask? I am Crimson
Rubeus, of the Black
Moon Clan.

225
00:18:16,554 --> 00:18:18,354
Why are you
after her?

226
00:18:18,621 --> 00:18:22,087
We are on a
mission to change
the future of
this metropolis.

227
00:18:22,121 --> 00:18:25,254
And the only
way for that to
happen is...

228
00:18:32,021 --> 00:18:35,421
...For her to die!

229
00:18:37,254 --> 00:18:38,521
[gasps]

230
00:18:38,554 --> 00:18:40,354
[yelling]

231
00:18:44,121 --> 00:18:46,054
[grunt]

232
00:18:46,421 --> 00:18:49,987
[gasp before
yelling in pain]

233
00:18:50,021 --> 00:18:51,254
[gasp]

234
00:18:54,221 --> 00:18:55,921
[grunt of pain]

235
00:18:55,954 --> 00:18:57,221
[laughter]

236
00:18:58,187 --> 00:19:02,121
Sailor Moon!
Sailor Moon!

237
00:19:04,321 --> 00:19:06,187
She's precocious...

238
00:19:07,421 --> 00:19:08,954
...Mischievous.

239
00:19:08,987 --> 00:19:11,887
And pretty annoying,
and yet...

240
00:19:12,921 --> 00:19:15,054
[soft crying]
Sailor Moon...

241
00:19:15,287 --> 00:19:17,954
...I can't seem to hate her.

242
00:19:21,187 --> 00:19:23,087
It's all over.

243
00:19:23,321 --> 00:19:25,054
[teary gasp]

244
00:19:25,087 --> 00:19:26,621
[sinister laughter]

245
00:19:26,987 --> 00:19:28,154
Not quite...

246
00:19:29,121 --> 00:19:31,587
...I refuse to be
defeated this easily.

247
00:19:32,521 --> 00:19:36,421
I will...
Protect her...

248
00:19:36,454 --> 00:19:37,454
...With my life!

249
00:19:37,687 --> 00:19:39,221
What?
[gasp]

250
00:19:40,154 --> 00:19:41,154
[surprised gasp]

251
00:19:42,154 --> 00:19:44,587
How dare you
go and threaten
such a young life?

252
00:19:44,621 --> 00:19:46,087
I won't
forgive you!

253
00:19:46,487 --> 00:19:47,921
Shut the
hell up!

254
00:19:48,687 --> 00:19:51,121
[grunt]

255
00:19:52,454 --> 00:19:55,221
[grunting and
battle cries]

256
00:19:55,921 --> 00:19:57,121
What?!

257
00:20:00,554 --> 00:20:02,954
[screaming in pain]

258
00:20:04,487 --> 00:20:09,354
Sailor Moon...you
are the only one
who can protect this
child. Do it.

259
00:20:09,387 --> 00:20:10,987
Right!

260
00:20:29,987 --> 00:20:38,087
Moon Princess...
Halation!

261
00:20:40,054 --> 00:20:43,087
[groaning in
pain]

262
00:20:44,387 --> 00:20:46,654
[in unison]
Master Rubeus!

263
00:20:46,687 --> 00:20:50,987
[grunt]
Spectre Sisters!
Retreat, now!

264
00:20:53,687 --> 00:20:57,521
In due time...
I'll have my
revenge!

265
00:21:04,387 --> 00:21:08,887
Hey, Chibi-Usa...
I want you to
tell me the truth.

266
00:21:09,154 --> 00:21:11,354
As far as I know
you came from the
future.

267
00:21:11,654 --> 00:21:16,354
But what did those
guys mean about the
tenth planet, and the
Black Moon Clan?

268
00:21:17,187 --> 00:21:19,221
And...what did
they do to your
mother?

269
00:21:19,454 --> 00:21:23,421
[sobbing]

270
00:21:24,187 --> 00:21:25,854
Sailor Moon!
[crying]

271
00:21:26,554 --> 00:21:30,087
Please Sailor Moon...
help my mommy...

272
00:21:30,621 --> 00:21:32,421
Save her from
those bad people!

273
00:21:33,921 --> 00:21:36,921
Puu told me that
I could count on
you and the other
Guardians to help me...

274
00:21:37,321 --> 00:21:44,421
[crying]
Please help
my mommy.

275
00:21:44,454 --> 00:21:46,321
Chibi-Usa...

276
00:21:46,354 --> 00:21:53,554
[quiet sobs]

277
00:21:58,921 --> 00:22:05,421
A flower no matter
how beautiful,
withers in the
course of time.

278
00:22:05,954 --> 00:22:07,154
So inevitably...

279
00:22:08,921 --> 00:22:13,421
...The beautiful Rabbit's
mother and the city of
Crystal Tokyo will have
the same ending...

280
00:22:13,954 --> 00:22:17,487
[maniacal laughter]

281
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:14,780
And then she's
awakened by a kiss
from a prince who
truly loves her!

282
00:24:15,014 --> 00:24:16,414
How romantic!

283
00:24:18,047 --> 00:24:20,180
I've heard it before.
Believing in fairy tales
in this day and age
is so childish.

284
00:24:20,214 --> 00:24:21,414
You're such a brat!

285
00:24:22,714 --> 00:24:25,614
Who says I believe in
fairy tales? I don't need
to. I have Mamo.

286
00:24:25,647 --> 00:24:27,414
Oh yeah? Well,
Mamo has a new
love.

287
00:24:27,647 --> 00:24:28,814
This is a
nightmare!

288
00:24:30,280 --> 00:24:34,447
Next time on
Sailor Moon R:
Awaken the Sleeping
Beauty: Mamoru's distress.

289
00:24:34,480 --> 00:24:36,561
The Moonlight
is a messenger
of love.

